tooltip.midas_gold.level.0: Can be folded in a smithing table, using Midas Gold Blocks
tooltip.midas_gold.level.1: You need quite a bit in order to unlock its true power...
tooltip.midas_gold.level.10: A magnificent weapon! Perhaps there is a way to go further...
tooltip.midas_gold.level.11: A Royal Upgrade to your blade
tooltip.midas_gold.level.12: If at first, you don't succeed...
tooltip.midas_gold.level.13: ... Try, try again. Then your courage should appear.
tooltip.midas_gold.level.14: The true power of the Royal Midas Gold Sword will only show...
tooltip.midas_gold.level.15: ... once you have reached the end of this journey.
tooltip.midas_gold.level.16: By folding over a thousand times, the swords blade becomes pure.
tooltip.midas_gold.level.17: That anything you defeat will grant you more of what you truly desire:
tooltip.midas_gold.level.19: The final stretch is upon you, you can do it!
tooltip.midas_gold.level.2: Over a hundred blocks. Impressive! Keep going!
tooltip.midas_gold.level.20: The incredible power of King Midas now rests within your blade!
tooltip.midas_gold.level.23: The incredible power of King Midas now rests within your blade...?
tooltip.midas_gold.level.24: Are you still applying Midas Gold to this sword?
tooltip.midas_gold.level.25: Why are you still applying Midas Gold to this sword???
tooltip.midas_gold.level.26: You already maxed its damage, you got the special ability
tooltip.midas_gold.level.27: Eventually you will just hit a cap or something
tooltip.midas_gold.level.28: Or maybe this goes on forever... I don't remember if such exists
tooltip.midas_gold.level.29: You might have taken a step back...
tooltip.midas_gold.level.3: Why would you make this many blocks? Just make normal gold...
tooltip.midas_gold.level.32: Can someone help me write more lines?
tooltip.midas_gold.level.33: You're telling me a Shrimp fried this rice...?
tooltip.midas_gold.level.34: If I may ask, how DID you get this much Midas Gold? Is your mob farm that efficient...?
tooltip.midas_gold.level.35: I hope you are macroing, since this amount of clicking could cause RSI
tooltip.midas_gold.level.36: Be sure to take breaks from pointlessly clicking in your Smithing Table
tooltip.midas_gold.level.37: At some point you WILL have to stop. You can't keep going like this
tooltip.midas_gold.level.38: If you won't, I will stop you. Just watch.
tooltip.midas_gold.level.39: Any second now, it will happen, trust.
